				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$55^{\circ }$$\end{document} latitude to north pole) from a dynamo simulation in which the dynamo operates a near-critical or weakly-supercritical regime (D/Dc=2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
